{"id":2074,"date":"2020-11-05T10:41:58","date_gmt":"2020-11-05T10:41:58","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/parliament.imarketing.com.na\/?page_id=2074"},"modified":"2021-09-09T14:46:41","modified_gmt":"2021-09-09T12:46:41","slug":"secretariat-nc","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/secretariat-nc\/","title":{"rendered":"Secretariat"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1620169142136{background-color: #f4f4f4 !important;}&#8221;]<div id=\"ultimate-heading-4346848a539219a7\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-4346848a539219a7 uvc-4521  uvc-heading-default-font-sizes\" data-hspacer=\"no_spacer\"  data-halign=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left\"><div class=\"uvc-heading-spacer no_spacer\" style=\"top\"><\/div><div class=\"uvc-main-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-4346848a539219a7 h2'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}' ><h2 style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Vision<\/h2><\/div><div class=\"uvc-sub-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-4346848a539219a7 .uvc-sub-heading '  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}'  style=\"font-weight:normal;\">To be a legislative Chamber that is accessible, discerning, representing citizens of all regions to ensure good governance and working vigorously for the Nation.<\/div><\/div><div id=\"ultimate-heading-41316848a53921aad\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-41316848a53921aad uvc-1842  uvc-heading-default-font-sizes\" data-hspacer=\"no_spacer\"  data-halign=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left\"><div class=\"uvc-heading-spacer no_spacer\" style=\"top\"><\/div><div class=\"uvc-main-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-41316848a53921aad h2'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}' ><h2 style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Mission Statement<\/h2><\/div><div class=\"uvc-sub-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-41316848a53921aad .uvc-sub-heading '  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}'  style=\"font-weight:normal;\">To review Bills and proposals passed to it by the National Assembly, ensuring that they substantively address regional concerns and that the Chamber\u2019s administrative services and oversight arrangements meet the high expectations of stakeholder.<\/p>\n<p>Core Values<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Impartiality<\/li>\n<li>Integrity<\/li>\n<li>Loyalty and Patriotism<\/li>\n<li>Professionalism<\/li>\n<li>Accountability<\/li>\n<li>Confidentiality<\/li>\n<li>Commitment<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div id=\"ultimate-heading-28426848a53921b3e\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-28426848a53921b3e uvc-6017  uvc-heading-default-font-sizes\" data-hspacer=\"no_spacer\"  data-halign=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left\"><div class=\"uvc-heading-spacer no_spacer\" style=\"top\"><\/div><div class=\"uvc-main-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-28426848a53921b3e h2'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}' ><h2 style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Who we are<\/h2><\/div><div class=\"uvc-sub-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-28426848a53921b3e .uvc-sub-heading '  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}'  style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The objective of the Secretariat is to provide effective and efficient service to Members through teamwork. To accomplish this noble objective the Secretary is assisted by the Management Team that comprises of all Heads of Directorates, Divisions and Sub-Divisions.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Management Team assists the Secretary with the implementation of policies and directives of the National Council. It also deliberates on matters affecting staff performance and conditions of service. The ultimate success of the National Council Administration thus hinges on the performance of this Team.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><\/div><div id=\"ultimate-heading-41216848a53921bc0\" class=\"uvc-heading ult-adjust-bottom-margin ultimate-heading-41216848a53921bc0 uvc-1073  uvc-heading-default-font-sizes\" data-hspacer=\"no_spacer\"  data-halign=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left\"><div class=\"uvc-heading-spacer no_spacer\" style=\"top\"><\/div><div class=\"uvc-main-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-41216848a53921bc0 h2'  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}' ><h2 style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Who we are<\/h2><\/div><div class=\"uvc-sub-heading ult-responsive\"  data-ultimate-target='.uvc-heading.ultimate-heading-41216848a53921bc0 .uvc-sub-heading '  data-responsive-json-new='{\"font-size\":\"\",\"line-height\":\"\"}'  style=\"font-weight:normal;\"><\/p>\n<div>\n<h2 class=\"contentheading\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Vision<\/span><\/strong><\/h2>\n<h2 class=\"contentheading\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-weight: normal;\">To be an accessible legislative chamber that represents citizens of all regions, ensuring good governance and working vigorously for the nation.<\/span><\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Mission Statement<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">To review bills and reports referred to it by the National Assembly, recommend legislation on\u00a0 matters of regional concerns and\u00a0 exercise oversight function to meet stakeholder\u2019s expectations.<\/div>\n<p><\/div><\/div>[vc_column_text][\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>[vc_row][vc_column css=&#8221;.vc_custom_1620169142136{background-color: #f4f4f4 !important;}&#8221;